= SDL_SetSurfaceBlendMode =
Use this function to set the blend mode used for blit operations.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_SetSurfaceBlendMode(SDL_Surface* surface,
                            int          blendMode)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''surface'''
|the surface / [[SDL_Surface]] to update
|-
|'''blendMode'''
|[[SDL_BlendMode]] to use for blit blending
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success, or -1 if the parameters are not valid; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

